# Provides a complete explanation of the meaning of the data element for human readability.  For the case of elements derived from existing elements (e.g. constraints), the definition SHALL be consistent with the base definition, but convey the meaning of the element in the particular context of use of the resource. (Note: The text you are reading is specified in ElementDefinition.definition).
#: StructureDefinition.element.RelatedPerson.identifier:passportLocal/definition
msgid "Local (internal) passport number, shared by the modern ID card and the older book-form passport. Set use = official for the credential currently in force (typically the ID card) and use = old for a superseded paper passport number."
msgstr "Mahalliy (ichki) passport raqami bo'lib, zamonaviy ID-karta va undan oldingi kitobcha ko'rinishidagi passport uchun umumiydir. Amaldagi hujjat uchun (odatda ID-karta) use = official, eskirgan qog'oz passport raqami uchun esa use = old qiymatini belgilang."

